From 7054327e3b3848ad436cd7a57e6e8fbed4893283 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Slick <slick@slicksync.local>
Date: Sat, 11 Jul 2026 20:00:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: label Activity feed entries with their Nuvio profile

v1.9.4 fixed getLibrary() to sync all Nuvio profiles, not just the
primary one. This tags every item with the profile it came from
(state.nuvioProfile in nuvio.js), threads that through
metricsProcessor.js into a new profileLabel column on
EpisodeWatchHistory/MovieWatchHistory, exposes it in the
recentActivity feed built by metricsBuilder.js, and renders it as a
small badge on Activity cards in both the grid and list views.

Nullable column addition, applied automatically via the existing
'prisma db push' step on container start - no manual migration
needed for the private SQLite deployment.

Bump to 1.9.5, changelog entry added.
